    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i just cut my arm pretty bad doing some prep for dinner and it keeps oozing blood even after i hold pressure on it for a bit. its a bit deep like i can see the edges pulling apart but i dont really want to go to the emergency room late at night if i dont have to. i read online that medical grade honey is great for healing wounds and keeps them clean, do u think i can just put some honey on it and bandage it up tight at home?",
